<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The amount of the Fund contribution in respect of the measures included in the special programme shall be paid to the Member State concerned (or in accordance with the instructions the latter communicates to this end to the Commission) according to the following rules: </inglise>
<eesti> Eriprogrammis sisalduvate meetmetega seotud fondimaksed tehakse asjaomasele liikmesriigile (v&otilde;i komisjonile juhiste kohaselt, mille liikmesriik on selleks andnud) j&auml;rgmiste eeskirjade kohaselt: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) expenditure incurred from the date of entry into force of this Regulation shall be eligible; </inglise>
<eesti> a) k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse j&otilde;ustumise kuup&auml;evast alates tehtavad kulutused on abik&otilde;lblikud; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) when there is a financial contribution by the Member State, payments, other than advance payments referred to in (c), shall be made as far as possible in parallel with the payment of the Member State's contribution. </inglise>
<eesti> b) liikmesriigi rahalise toetuse korral tehakse maksed, v&auml;lja arvatud punktis c osutatud ettemaksed, v&otilde;imalikult &uuml;heaegselt liikmesriigi maksega. </eesti>
<inglise> In any other case, payments shall be made when the Member State certifies that the payment is due and may be paid by the Community. </inglise>
<eesti> K&otilde;ikidel muudel juhtudel tehakse maksed siis, kui liikmesriik t&otilde;endab, et makse kuulub maksmisele ning &uuml;hendus v&otilde;ib seda maksta. </eesti>
<inglise> Each request for payment shall be accompanied by a statement from the Member State certifying the operation and the existence of detailed supporting documents, and shall contain the following information: </inglise>
<eesti> K&otilde;ikidele maksetaotlustele lisatakse liikmesriigi avaldus, millega t&otilde;endatakse toimingu tegemist ja &uuml;ksikasjalike t&auml;iendavate dokumentide olemasolu ning mis sisaldab j&auml;rgmist teavet: </eesti>
<inglise> - the nature of the operations covered by the payment claim; </inglise>
<eesti> - maksen&otilde;udega h&otilde;lmatud toimingute laad; </eesti>
<inglise> - particulars of the amount and nature of expenditure paid in respect of the different operations during the period covered by the claim; </inglise>
<eesti> - &uuml;ksikasjad n&otilde;udega h&otilde;lmatud ajavahemikul toimingutega seoses tehtud kulutuste suuruse ja laadi kohta; </eesti>
<inglise> - confirmation that the operations described in the payment claim have been begun in accordance with the special programme; </inglise>
<eesti> - kinnitus selle kohta, et maksen&otilde;udes kirjeldatud toiminguid on vastavalt eriprogrammile alustatud; </eesti>
<inglise> (c) on production by the Member State concerned of written evidence that the special programme has already occasioned expenditure under an annual tranche, the Fund may, at the State's request, make an advance of 30 % of the appropriations committed. </inglise>
<eesti> c) kui asjaomane liikmesriik esitab kirjaliku t&otilde;endi selle kohta, et seoses eriprogrammiga on iga-aastase osamakse alusel juba kulutusi tehtud, v&otilde;ib fond liikmesriigi taotlusel anda ettemaksena 30% eraldatud assigneeringutest. </eesti>
<inglise> When the amount of this advance has been exhausted and when the Member State has forwarded to the Commission the certificate referred to in (b), further successive advance payments may be made, each of 30 % of the appropriations committed for each annual tranche. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui k&otilde;nealune ettemakse on kulutatud ja kui liikmesriik on esitanud komisjonile punktis b osutatud t&otilde;endi, v&otilde;ib teha j&auml;rgmisi ettemakseid, millest iga&uuml;ks on 30% iga-aastaseks osamakseks eraldatud assigneeringutest. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> At the end of each year, the Member State concerned shall present to the Commission a report on the progress made in carrying out the special programme by reference to the information required in the Annex to this Regulation. </inglise>
<eesti> Asjaomane liikmesriik esitab iga aasta l&otilde;pul komisjonile aruande eriprogrammi elluviimisel tehtud edusammude kohta, tuginedes k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse lisas n&otilde;utud andmetele. </eesti>
<inglise> These reports should enable the Commission to satisfy itself that the special programme is being executed, to observe its effects and to establish that the different operations are being carried out in a coherent manner. </inglise>
<eesti> K&otilde;nealuste aruannete p&otilde;hjal peab komisjon saama veenduda eriprogrammi t&auml;ideviimises, j&auml;lgida selle m&otilde;jusid ja korraldada toimingute j&auml;rjekindla elluviimise. </eesti>
